This is waly v. 0.1
waly is the wavelet library for yorick
for now waly is mostly wrappers to the gsl_wavelet library
see check_waly.i for exemples of use
first install libgsl and libgsl-dev package
modify PKG_DEPLIBS and PKG_CFLAGS in makefile accordingly
then yorick -batch make.i && make && make install
have fun !

